    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. There are noticeable engine performance issues, the transmission shifts roughly, and there is visible rust on the undercarriage and body panels. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is best suited as a project car or for parts, and I strongly recommend a professional inspection before purchase.",
