      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It's been my absolute baby, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered every single week. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new and drives like a dream, you've found it. Come take a look and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
